name: Taurus in its power color
description:
Taurus (April 20–May 20): Green 

Go out and take on the world with your zodiac power color that amplifies your inherent nature and boosts your confidence to express yourself more freely. 

Taurus is an earth sign and, as such, connects deeply with the color green. “Green is great for inspiring Taurus to tap into their innate prosperity and their gift of creating abundance,” Terrones says. Taurus is rich in life and splendor like a verdant, lush forest. Their surroundings should represent and reinforce that concept to make them feel at home and share that beauty with others. From lovely houseplants to luxurious jade stone, green will help Taurus look and feel their best.
